flowchart TB
  subgraph Browser Runtime
    App[Kernel / Studio]
    OPFS[Origin Private File System]
    WASM[SQLite WASM runtime]
  end

  subgraph Storage Adapter Layer
    A[OPFSSQLiteAdapter]
    MIG[runMigrations]
    CRUD[execute/query/transaction]
  end

  subgraph Data Model
    G[JSON-LD node]
    N[(nodes table)]
    MG[(migrations table)]
  end

  App --> A
  A --> MIG
  A --> CRUD

  MIG --> MG
  CRUD --> N

  A --> WASM
  WASM --> OPFS

  G --> CRUD
  CRUD --> G
